---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — LuxeDate" description="Privacy policy for LuxeDate." active="/privacy">
  <Section eyebrow="LEGAL" title="Privacy Policy" subtitle="Draft policy for beta. Not legal advice.">
    <Card class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-p:text-white/70 prose-li:text-white/70 prose-strong:text-white">
      <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> March 9, 2026</p>
      <p>LuxeDate ("we," "us") provides a waitlist and beta alert service for curated recommendations. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information.</p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact information</strong> such as email address and optional details you submit (neighborhoods, preferences).</li>
        <li><strong>Usage information</strong> such as pages visited and form interactions to understand site performance.</li>
        <li><strong>Communications</strong> you send us and our replies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate the waitlist and beta program</li>
        <li>Personalize alerts and improve recommendation quality</li>
        <li>Communicate product updates and access invites</li>
        <li>Maintain safety, prevent abuse, and comply with law</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we share information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information.</li>
        <li>We may share information with service providers (hosting, analytics) under confidentiality obligations.</li>
        <li>We may disclose information if required by law or to protect rights and safety.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>We keep information as long as needed for the waitlist/beta program and legitimate business purposes, then delete or anonymize it.</p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can unsubscribe from beta updates at any time.</li>
        <li>You can request deletion by contacting <strong>support@luxedate.example</strong> (replace with your real email).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>We use reasonable safeguards to protect your information, but no method is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>LuxeDate is not intended for children under 13 (or under 16 where applicable).</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy. The latest version will be posted on this page.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Email: <strong>support@luxedate.example</strong></p>
    </Card>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
